membersInfo.bio: Web Application Developer with 10+ years experience in modern, full-stack, component-based design with a focus on reliability via automated testing. Extremely diverse history in getting up to speed quickly and utilizing many different technologies to solve real-world problems. Diverse portfolio of applications includes an online document viewer, inventory management software, online health care tracking apps, and social network visualization and analysis.
